Package: greyforecasting
Type: Package
Title: A package for grey systems forecasting methods
Version: 0.1.4
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Ning",
             family = "Xu",
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "nuaa_xuning@163.com"))
Description: This package provide a series of tools for grey forecasting methods, one of the components of grey system theory. Functions such as gm(), dgm() complete all computation and retrive a S3 variable containing the model results, the class is named as 'greyforecasting'. In addtion, plot() and summary() functions are used to process the model variable. 
